This solution is also based on SO user Thomas&#39; helpful code [here](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/20535199/onvif-beginning-of-device-discovery). I&#39;ve mostly just simplified his code by removing the threading, and added some comments. Again his solution is probably better than mine (more performant); BUT, mine may be more understandable for a beginner (like me).

Here is the code:  

