Basically you should build and return `Mono&lt;Map&lt;Map&lt;String, List&lt;String&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;`

You&#39;re getting an array because you&#39;re returing `Flux` which means &quot;many elements&quot;

But since`Mono&lt;Map&lt;Map&lt;String, List&lt;String&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;` is not readable, it is better to create a dto class like this:

    @Data
    @AllArgsConstructor
    @NoArgsConstructor
    public class Response {
    
        @JsonUnwrapped
        private Shipment shipment;
    
        @Data
        @AllArgsConstructor
